WEBVTT

00:00.143 --> 00:01.348
Sahaja Yoga

00:01.373 --> 00:05.602
It's founder is now in Turkey and speaking only with us.

00:05.627 --> 00:07.920
Who is she? Shri Mataji.

00:07.952 --> 00:11.285
Listen to what she is saying.

00:12.201 --> 00:19.476
All those watching me, if they have a desire,
should open their hands like this.

00:19.501 --> 00:25.729
Put your right hand on your heart and say inside,

00:25.769 --> 00:34.161
"Mother, I am not this mind, this body, these feelings,

00:34.248 --> 00:36.808
these conditionings".

00:36.865 --> 00:39.700
I am the pure spirit.

00:39.730 --> 00:47.012
We are carrying a feeling  of guilt inside.

00:47.052 --> 00:53.466
But it is harmful to this center here.

00:53.517 --> 00:57.202
Now stretch your right hand towards Me like this.

00:57.227 --> 01:01.558
and put your left hand above your  head.

01:01.583 --> 01:06.424
And see carefully if you feel a cool or a hot breeze

01:06.449 --> 01:11.860
You can close your eyes if you like.

01:11.958 --> 01:16.809
Now stretch your left hand towards Me.

01:16.921 --> 01:20.993
and check with your right hand above your head.

01:21.018 --> 01:25.573
Do you feel a cool or a hot breeze?

01:25.653 --> 01:28.398
You can move your hand slowly up or down.

01:28.438 --> 01:33.305
Now raise your both hands.

01:33.330 --> 01:40.495
And ask one of these questions from your heart.

01:40.520 --> 01:45.895
Mother, is what I have felt the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?

01:45.938 --> 01:49.174
Or Mother, is this the Spirit?

01:49.206 --> 01:55.867
Or Mother, is this the all pervading power of Divine Love?

01:55.892 --> 01:59.464
Now look at Me but don't think.

01:59.489 --> 02:03.842
And you will feel a cool or a hot breeze on your hands.

02:03.867 --> 02:09.867
also  you can feel it above your fontanel bone area.

02:09.892 --> 02:16.546
This is the moment when your spirit starts to grow.

02:19.943 --> 02:22.831
How Long you will stay  in Turkey

02:22.856 --> 02:24.823
I'm going on Monday

02:31.313 --> 02:32.734
Did you like Turkey.

02:32.806 --> 02:33.937
Of course

02:34.870 --> 02:36.099
very much.

02:41.121 --> 02:44.654
In very short time we are waiting you again in Turkey

02:44.687 --> 02:48.160
Ohh, I think, next time I will came for a long time.

02:50.688 --> 02:55.194
That those were felt the  cool breeze should write the letter

02:55.219 --> 02:58.107
for should inform them it will be a good idea

03:16.636 --> 03:20.477
But it is spring time now, there is no one
who does not fee a breeze above one's head.

03:20.541 --> 03:26.763
In generally, people in the world are not happy
with their life and with themselves.

03:26.818 --> 03:30.684
Everything they want happens
they earn money

03:30.709 --> 03:34.110
but however still somehow people do not become happy

03:34.135 --> 03:35.295
they do not fee happy inside.

03:35.328 --> 03:39.236
As it was said in the Koran, Mirage has to take place.

03:39.349 --> 03:42.516
The ascend has to be

03:44.535 --> 03:47.559
and a transformation has  to give

03:51.261 --> 03:56.031
Prophet Mohammed has said,
you will feel your spirit on your fingertips.

03:56.056 --> 04:00.123
and you will know yourself
you will face yourself.

04:00.171 --> 04:02.342
This reality you should know.

04:11.260 --> 04:13.997
Christ never went to any  university

04:14.775 --> 04:18.975
Some people , for example Christ never went to any univertsity.

04:19.008 --> 04:21.973
Mohammed did not to even know how to read and write.

04:24.110 --> 04:27.292
When you are standing in the water
you may be afraid of the waves.

04:27.317 --> 04:30.308
But you are standing in a boat

04:30.333 --> 04:34.532
you will watch the waves and enjoy them.

04:34.582 --> 04:37.821
But if you can swim, you are not afraid of the water.

04:37.846 --> 04:41.326
you can jump into the water and save people there.

04:41.351 --> 04:45.077
As Shri Mataji loves people, she also likes flowers.

04:45.118 --> 04:47.785
Is there any special flower She identifies Herself with?

04:47.817 --> 04:50.674
My name  is also daisy

04:53.191 --> 04:54.571
margarita

04:59.283 --> 05:02.147
thank you very much, thank you.

05:04.333 --> 05:05.174
Beautiful.

05:05.198 --> 05:06.928
It is the eye of  Shri Fatima

05:06.953 --> 05:08.428
I know, I know.
